nodes.text: Mos Eisley Customs was a customs organization working in Mos Eisley on the planet Tatooine. In the wake of Han Solo's hasty departure from the city, Mos Eisley Customs stepped up the number of inspections it performed. Mos Eisley Customs also impounded Big Bunji's starship when it was discovered to be smuggling droid espionage matrixes.
